 1. The reason your GUI is wired is causing, your frame.pack() method is in the ```for``` loop.
 2. Why you&#39;re setting the layout of the BorderPanel(JPanel) to BorderLayout? remove that line. Let it be FlowLayout.
 3. I recommend not to use so many setPrefferedSize() methods, Let the frames and JPanel&#39;s Layout Manager do the work.

